Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:30.22,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Kuuhaku no yoru mo kuru hazu no nai asa mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:34.97,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Zenbu wakattetanda
